headline: A Look Back at Beverages, Alcohol, and Tobacco Stocks’ Q1 Earnings: Vita Coco (NASDAQ:COCO) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
summary: As the Q1 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the beverages, alcohol, and tobacco industry, including Vita Coco (NASDAQ:COCO) and its peers.
